{"type": "article", "id": 61760, "title": "Valentino 用诗句装点秀场，以及，MLGB 商标被判无效 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2019-03-05T09:16:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1580, "name": "巴黎时装周"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190305171526HBFc8z5YdSyr1ipV.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻</h3><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.bjnews.com.cn/news/2019/03/03/552372.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">潮流品牌 MLGB 商标终审被判无效，法院认定“格调不高”</a></strong> | 李晨和潘玮柏的潮流品牌“MLGB”商标于 2010 年 12 月 15 日申请注册，2011 年 12 月 28 日被核准注册。但 2015 年 10 月 9 日，第三人（四位律师）向工商部门提出对该商标的质疑。2016 年 12 月 “MLGB”商标被工商部门宣告无效。该品牌主体公司上海俊客不服，指出“MLGB”意为“My Life’s Getting Better”，随后就商标一事上诉至北京知识产权法院、北京高级人民法院。北京知识产权法院于 2017 年 11 月驳回了上诉，北京高级人民法院则于今年 3 月 3 日宣布驳回上诉，维持原判。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.msn.com/en-ca/lifestyle/travel/article/christian-louboutin-to-open-hotel-in-portugal-in-2020/ar-BBUmy6Q\" rel=\"nofollow\">“红底鞋”品牌 Christian Louboutin 将于 2020 年在葡萄牙开设首家酒店</a>&nbsp;</strong>| 该酒店由建筑师 Madalena Caiado 主持设计，将于今年 4 月开始建造，设有餐厅及 21 间客房，预计将于 2020 年夏天开业。此前，Christian Louboutin 已涉足美妆及童鞋等领域。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20190304005127/en/Inter-Parfums-Reports-2018-Fourth-Quarter-Year\" rel=\"nofollow\">香水制造商 Inter Parfums 去年净利润增长 26%，主要靠 Coach 推动</a>&nbsp;</strong>| 2018 财年 Inter Parfums 集团销售额同比增长 14% 至 6.97 亿美元，净利润同比增长 26% 至 691 万美元。该集团 CEO Jean Madar 在财报中称，Coach 香水业务是主要推动力，去年 5 款香水销售额达 1 亿美元，同比增幅达 73%。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://fashionista.com/2019/03/glossier-play-makeup-products-launch\" rel=\"nofollow\">Glossier 推出支线品牌 Glossier Play。</a></strong></p><p>这个新的子品牌主打高饱和、多选择的彩妆产品，于 3 月 4 日发布了首批 4 款产品： “Colorslide”眼线胶笔，14 色可选；“Vinylic Lip”漆式唇彩，6 色可选；“Glitter Gelée”胶状眼影，4 色可选；“Niteshine”高光，4 色可选。单价从 14 至 20 美元不等。</p><p>Glossier 由美妆博主 Emily Weiss 于 2014 年推出。根据她向媒体公布的数据，该品牌 2018 年营收超过 1 亿美元。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305164316BHkZqQyGCo5FDlaV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305164318LdMnYQWkTevUlxpt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305164319NTfJa4whpqB9j8Xt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903051643138Pjap24xdgcfSsFk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.315789\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/fashion/403284/off-white-tuichuniuzishuipingshounadaixilieshoujia-920-meijin/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Off-White 推出牛仔水瓶收纳袋系列。</a></strong></p><p>白色售价为 920 美元，黑色为 810 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305160516al2bgMLDUZIWAv4f.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.674107\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305160532otlCMTAra1cRbX8J.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.674107\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305160540lMWb8UGXvQ6OB37r.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.674107\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305160548gCEi5r9zUWFHdqsl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.674107\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/fashion/403363/yifanchuanhetiaosanyundongweilinggany-3-fabu-2019-chunxiaquanfuyinhuaxilie/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Y-3 发布 2019 春夏全幅印花系列。</a></strong><br></p><p>大廓形、全幅印花设计的灵感来自帆船和跳伞运动，面料采用防水处理的光滑尼龙，领口和下摆处的抽绳设计则增强了服装的多变性。该系列将于 3 月 7 日在 Y-3 全球旗舰店、官网&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://y-3.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Y-3.com</a>&nbsp;和特选零售商处发售。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903051603114D0q5xhapeKw1m8t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600089\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305160308Zp9zcLoEYfB2egHO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600079\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903051603054YecXPrgGwKp9EUq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600189\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305161138DMXsfRaFW7rVxhtO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599906\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305161149HQmSk9BfNxU3nG26.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599906\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305161145zYmtSvfVesZIuCAn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599906\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305161146fWQauvxUZ6RzricL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599906\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305160308bF31tHMg76v4eYwk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599906\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903051603082PAJhTLcjspxSyDg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599927\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>巴黎时装周继续。</strong></p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/fall-ready-to-wear-2019/paris/valentino/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Balenciaga 2019 秋冬：</a></strong></p><p>Demna Gvasalia 在秀场上铺满了沥青，灯光从天花板上方不断闪烁，让模特们在光影中忽隐忽现。<br></p><p>新系列比以往都庞大得多，有 109 套 look。Demna Gvasalia 特别强调这是一个“巴黎主题”的系列，重在将巴黎人的穿着风格用一种更现代的方式表达出来。因此在这个系列中你虽然会看到一些熟悉的元素——夸张的肩线、随处可见的 Logo——但它将更多焦点放在了剪裁和廓形上，减少了街头感，比以往看上去更加精细。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154451vf4jwso3Zhe0QFOV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154448DanlJCKdrQucze8N.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154448PbLfrvlDwNpIiRZ8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154448MPmowRGcsL3i56JC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154449kcPI65EBnNHyUGRt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154449CZ18MftBPHkJGXcu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154458lMbGdpkmZC3PgznI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903051544509vLjEgapoBnF2qKw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154451GygOBIqCPNr69cvh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154451M92bwsRgxiL8lBcG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154451kSzycha0vdD3IXCQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154452KNUYbhsmQzyueRql.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154453PHmro69xW3nDCiVT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154454eM5p1RhgJjGlFWIU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903051544545WTwnjv9IGJ6Pctp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154454LIW0RUMPm9fskdJa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154455dWCiBaGufkyj043n.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154455i1fxaFnQYg86CqSD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154456NubE6hm7O9ZfYDow.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903051544566fXVAclnoZzd9NFa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154457FySwLqln5Ya90sND.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903051544582PWsVmytlCBYvD7h.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154458myxrznGQ0ZDlhCbF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154458BmEeA3U0GyP1ZrJc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2019030515450006EukwiAe53XgDaI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154502V478JL0ZP5WtGIre.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154500s1TI4nHluRFaME72.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154501CRJb5GFcaKynf2iV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/fall-ready-to-wear-2019/paris/valentino/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valentino 2019 秋冬：</a></strong></p><p>“你所爱之人会成为内心的幽灵，你以这种方式让他们活了下去。”（The people you love become ghosts inside of you, and like this you keep them alive.）</p><p>这个霓虹灯牌是艺术家&nbsp;Robert Montgomery 的装置艺术代表作“People You Love”。它原本放在室外，这次被创意总监 Pierpaolo Piccioli 搬进了秀场。除 这位艺术家外，Pierpaolo Piccioli 还找来三位诗人 Yrsa Daley-Ward、Greta Bellamacina、Mustafa The Poet，讨论爱和自我表达的力量，并将她们的诗句集结在新一册&nbsp;Valentino ON LOVE<em>&nbsp;</em>中，作为邀请函发放给了嘉宾。</p><p>新系列中最引人注目的印花图案由 Undercover 设计师高桥盾所设计，将一座 19 世纪新古典主义的恋人雕塑与流行朋克风格的玫瑰图案结合在了一起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305161634h4IAWuNZzQy2LPBp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305161749OqeMJWPuRT57fX0d.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.999074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154256VXwZHta5jbBri4Jk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154256LgrbeVM6Y45okpJT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154259GyeHvgRqF8uYsclJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154258814YFHvKGdDCusUg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154259SN2V6ysMtJlXkAIv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154301xUomGdVWFM9HPvqe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154301a76H3EnGWFuzPBUv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154302bLkYtICQD5zsgcp4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154302ZKgkf3BxCGjYeUST.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903051543029UYKoaMrpfGWeOvS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154305LFrjAO3BT0RECz68.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154305gvxAqeP1jOYVGy97.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154305qbQnte10Tu4ENOF5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154306gPalj3NTqnoEr7kB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154306uJ4itcL6avbPz8xp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154307oAKqtY0zD9Bdp25l.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/fall-ready-to-wear-2019/paris/sacai/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sacai 2019 秋冬：</a></strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903051548277G5y9u3wP4fWQItb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154825daq6SARI7Jgm3VTj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154825Mr0BpwI2HacADNQE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305154825c4YM6sSCaB